title: Dreams are now a reality! Res Lease in San Marcos. 2 Beds, 1 Baths
posting_body: ['Schedule your tour today to lease this incredible 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom duplex in San Marcos, TX!', 'Located near accessible highways, San Marcos Regional Airport and shopping venues.', 'The lovely home entrance welcomes you to the spacious family living room with tile flooring and a ceiling fan to keep you cool in the hot Texas months.', 'The cozy kitchen could make any home chef happy, with ample wood cabinetry, and plenty of counter space to utilize.', 'It also gives easy access to the backyard, ideal for any cook-outs with your loved ones.', 'The primary bedroom has a ceiling fan as well as a walk-in closet, a full bathroom with double vanity, and a large tiled shower; perfect to relax after a long day of work.', "Don't forget to check out its amazing fenced backyard!!", 'The large, luscious area is ideal for hosting friends, and family on those joyous occasions!', 'Apply and tour today, it will lease fast!!', '**', 'All renters are enrolled in the resident benefits package- reach out for more details.', ' ***Please Text FEDERICO to', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Federico Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 7838427)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
